<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About New Brighton</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">The New Brighton Community maintains a community hall, with wheelchair access, meeting rooms and a kitchen.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">In cooperation with the City of Calgary, the association also offers recreation facilities, including tennis courts, an outdoor hockey and skating rink, a soccer and baseball field and an outdoor water park.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">The association offers various community programs, including tot and youth soccer, a running club and a Jelly Bean dance.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">The community is also an active Block Watch neighbourhood.</p>
        </div>
